  15.11.1999    V0.7    Tilfřjet GUI (Amiga type for nu).
            Tilfřjet Microsoft ADPCM audio codec (for AVI).
            Tilfřjet Microsoft Video 1 8-bit (MSVC/CRAM/WHAM) codec.
            Tilfřjet Apple Graphics (SMC) video codec (for QT).
